oneliner to find potential SQL injection

cat urls.txt | shuf | httpx -mc 200 | qsreplace "'" | shuf | httpx -fs 200 -sc > sqli_no_200.txt

the command makes a list of urls where inserting the quote changed the status of the response. Errors 50X and 302 are good signs of sqli.
